sentences: Kim Ji-won (Korean: 김지원; born December 21, 1995), known by his stage name Bobby (Korean: 바비) is a South Korean rapper, singer-songwriter and member of iKon under YG Entertainment.
In 2016, he formed a sub-unit with Mino under the name MOBB.
Kim Ji-won was born on December 21, 1995 in Seoul, South Korea.

sentences: In 2005, his family moved to Fairfax, Virginia, United States.
